at I’d like to see for all plugins.','This review plugin came about as a consequence of collecting a business’s opening times for a London-based web client. There was plenty of relevant data for the business offered by the Places API from Google — with data from Google Maps and Google My Business. The recent review data is available and, with some tweaks, it could be displayed anywhere in a similar style to Google’s reviews pop-up in the search results.'=>'This review plugin came about as a consequence of collecting a business’ opening times for a London-based web client. There was plenty of relevant data for the business offered by the Places API from Google – with data from Google Maps and Google My Business. The recent review data is available and, with some tweaks, it could be displayed anywhere in a similar style to Google’s reviews pop-up in the search results.','In the carousel, set a specific number of slides to play. The carousel must active with the following parameters: <a href="%1$s">%2$s</a> and <a href="%3$s">%4$s</a>.'=>'In the carousel, set a specific number of slides to play. The carousel must be active with the following parameters: <a href="%1$s">%2$s</a> and <a href="%3$s">%4$s</a>.','en, fr, de, …'=>'en, fr, de, …','No reviews imported.'=>'No reviews imported.','Import empty reviews'=>'Import empty reviews','This plugin is not fully set up. Please ask your administrator to complete the process.'=>'This plugin is not fully set up. Please ask your administrator to complete the process.','Please ask your administrator to set up this plugin using our <a href="%s" class="components-external-link" target="_blank">visual guide</a>.'=>'Please ask your administrator to set up this plugin using our <a href="%s" class="components-external-link" target="_blank">visual guide</a>.','You do not have sufficient permission to perform this action.'=>'You do not have sufficient permissions to perform this action.','Google Reviews'=>'Google Reviews','Successfully u