 the entire shortcode provided that no reviews are listed. This will already be applied in some instances.','Apply style sheet colors to SVG vector images in the overall rating stars. Alternatively, use the parameter: <a href="%1$s">%2$s</a> or <a href="%3$s">%4$s</a>.'=>'Apply style sheet colours to SVG vector images in the overall rating stars. Alternatively, use the parameter: <a href="%1$s">%2$s</a> or <a href="%3$s">%4$s</a>.','Use HTML entities rather than SVG vector images in the overall rating stars. Alternatively, use the parameter: <a href="%1$s">%2$s</a> or <a href="%3$s">%4$s</a>.'=>'Use HTML entities rather than SVG vector images in the overall rating stars. Alternatively, use the parameter: <a href="%1$s">%2$s</a> or <a href="%3$s">%4$s</a>.','Override the default Google icon with a monochrome black version. Used for tiny badges and links.'=>'Override the default Google icon with a monochrome black version. Used for tiny badges and links.','Override the default Google icon with a monochrome white version. Used for tiny badges and links.'=>'Override the default Google icon with a monochrome white version. Used for tiny badges and links.','Used with stripe to offer a more contrasting version of the alternating backgrounds with dark/light text.'=>'Used with stripe to offer a more contrasting version of the alternating backgrounds with dark/light text.','Alternatively stripe the main sections with alternating backgrounds.'=>'Alternatively stripe the main sections with alternating backgrounds.','Useful for badge — remove the outline effect (box-shadow). Helpful if you want to use a parent element’s styling.'=>'Useful for badge – remove the outline effect (box-shadow). Helpful if you want to use a parent element’s styling.','Useful for badge and tiny themes — fill the background with a solid color that works with light or dark. Recommend using your own styling to set a specific color.'=>'Useful for badge and tiny themes - fill the background with a solid colour that works with light or dark. Recommend using your own styling to set a specific colour.','Review text can be justified — works better with narrow spaces or columns.'=>'Review text can be justified - works better with narrow spaces or columns.','Set to four columns, must be used with columns class.'=>'Set to four columns, must be used with columns class.','Set to three columns, must be used with columns class.'=>'Set to three columns, must be used with columns class.','Set to two columns, must be used with columns class.'=>'Set to two columns, must be used with columns class.','Centrally align all text and elements. Can be applied to any theme but some may already share its styling.'=>'Centrally align all text and elements. Can be applied to any theme but some may already share its styling.','If the shortcode is placed in a narrow container and text or elements are jumping to a new lines, try applying this class to handle the narrow space in a neater fashion.'=>'If the shortcode is placed in a narrow container and text or elements are jumping to a new lines, try applying this class to handle the narrow space in a neater fashion.','Even smaller styling of fonts with some elements hidden by default. Works well with badge to summarize your business’ listing on Google. Recommend setting your own max-width value in your style sheet.'=>'Even smaller styling of fonts with some elements hidden by default. Works well with badge to summarise your business’ listing on Google. Recommend setting your own max-width value in your style sheet.','A more compact version to summarize your business’ listing on Google, better without reviews.'=>'A more compact version to summarise your business’ listing on Google, better without reviews.','Uses fonts, styling and sizing found in the Google review listings.'=>'Uses fonts, styling and sizing found in the Google review listings.','For pages or sections with dark backgrounds — some text and icons have their colors inverted compared to 