an>. Any sequence length accepted; separated by commas for: heading, vicinity, rating, list, list item, buttons, attribution and errors.'=>'Set your own HTML tags for elements such as replacing <span class="code">%1$s</span> with <span class="code">%2$s</span>. Any sequence length accepted; separated by commas for: heading, vicinity, rating, list, list item, buttons, attribution and errors.','Show or hide the &ldquo;powered by Google&rdquo; attribution.'=>'Show or hide the &ldquo;powered by Google&rdquo; attribution.','/url/to/image.jpg'=>'/url/to/image.jpg','Show or hide users’ avatars — or specify your own [single] image replacement (jpg, jpeg, png, gif, svg extensions are supported).'=>'Show or hide users’ avatars – or specify your own [single] image replacement (jpg, jpeg, png, gif, and svg extensions are supported).','Show a link/button to allow a visitor to leave a review at Google. Specify custom text string to appear as the link text. This is hidden by default.'=>'Show a link/button to allow a visitor to leave a review at Google. Specify custom text string to appear as the link text. This is hidden by default.','Show a link/button for all reviews listed externally at Google. Specify custom text string to appear as the link text. This is hidden by default.'=>'Show a link/button for all reviews listed externally at Google. Specify custom text string to appear as the link text. This is hidden by default.','URL string'=>'URL string','Set the entire element as a link to all reviews listed externally at Google (only if no reviews listed). Automatically added to Badge theme when no reviews are showing.'=>'Set the entire element as a link to all reviews listed externally at Google (only if no reviews listed). Automatically added to Badge theme when no reviews are showing.','Text to use in the &ldquo;more&rdquo; toggle link.'=>'Text to use in the &ldquo;more&rdquo; toggle link.','Characters in review text to show before a &ldquo;more&rdquo; toggle link is shown to expand the remainder of the review. Empty (<span class="code">%s</span>) = no excerpt; show all review text.'=>'Characters in review text to show before a &ldquo;more&rdquo; toggle link is shown to expand the remainder of the review. Empty (<span class="code">%s</span>) = no excerpt; show all review text.','Filter out reviews containing a specific word or words. Case insensitive; full word match. Multiple required words as a comma separated list.'=>'Filter out reviews containing a specific word or words. Case insensitive; full word match. Multiple required words as a comma separated list.','Require a specific word or words in review text. Case insensitive; full word match. Multiple required words as a comma separated list.'=>'Require a specific word or words in review text. Case insensitive; full word match. Multiple required words as a comma separated list.','Filter by a maximum review text character count. Empty (<span class="code">%1$s</span>) = no maximum. <span class="code">%2$s</span> = no review text. '=>'Filter by a maximum review text character count. Empty (<span class="code">%1$s</span>) = no maximum. <span class="code">%2$s</span> = no review text. ','Filter by a minimum review text character count. Empty (<span class="code">%1$s</span>) or <span class="code">%2$s</span> = no minimum. '=>'Filter by a minimum review text character count. Empty (<span class="code">%1$s</span>) or <span class="code">%2$s</span> = no minimum. ','Show or hide all review text leaving just the names, ratings and relative times.'=>'Show or hide all review text leaving just the names, ratings and relative times.','Animate the rating stars on view, load or set as static (<span class="code">%s</span>).'=>'Animate the rating stars on view, load, or set as static (<span class="code">%s</span>).','Any valid string'=>'Any valid string','Word displayed after the total review/rating count number in the summary. Accepts %1$s to set placement of review/rating count (e.g. <em>Tenemos %1$s com